{"tid":1988294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌稱下月7日前沒異常社區爆發可考慮逐步放寬限制","createTime":"2020-04-25T06:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T08:25:19.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6c493d75184bf8befdacebecd641204d2f69ce","tid":1988294,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"政府抗疫督導委員會專家顧問許樹昌表示，現階段不敢說本港新型肺炎疫情已受控，因為日前一宗本地感染個案，仍未找到感染源頭。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌說，若果下月7日前再沒有異常的社區爆發，或者只有零星可以追蹤到源頭的本地個案，最快可考慮在下月7日逐步放寬社交距離限制，例如公務員回復辦公室上班、中學生復課，至於小學生及幼稚園則最好下學年才復課。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522677-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522677-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=439a9b6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522677-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=99602ac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522677-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;最快可考慮在下月7日逐步放寬社交距離限制&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請問包唔包括重開體育館、健身中心、戲院、K房?</span><br />\n<br />\n&quot;小學生及幼稚園則最好下學年才復課&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔知有無家長會抱怨令子女學習進度嚴重受影響?</span>"},{"pid":"ef54280a16666a8e0b95f4fd77b84d99e467ea82","tid":1988294,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"我要做gym<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef006e0324884b6cba5935cabbd8ad8705ea75a6","tid":1988294,"uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T08:25:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522669-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522669-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKiZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=87b6c8c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522669-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0a82252b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522669-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n&quot;現時本港大約有5%的患者需入住深切治療部，但當年沙士有四分一患者需深切治療部&quot;<br />\n&quot;現時很多仍然留院的病人都很精神，毋須利用儀器供氧，甚至可以在病房玩電話或做運動，只是等待病毒檢測呈陰性反應&quot;<br />\n&quot;病人失去味覺和嗅覺的情況都很短暫，亦只有少部分病人有肺部纖維化情況&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>都話左疫情被誇大啦</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}